30#include <signal.h>
31#include <stdlib.h>
32#include <unistd.h>
33
34#include <atf-c.h>
35
36ATF_TC_WITHOUT_HEAD(pass_and_pass);
37ATF_TC_BODY(pass_and_pass, tc)
38{
39 atf_tc_expect_pass();
40}
41
42ATF_TC_WITHOUT_HEAD(pass_but_fail_requirement);
43ATF_TC_BODY(pass_but_fail_requirement, tc)
44{
45 atf_tc_expect_pass();
46 atf_tc_fail("Some reason");
47}
48
49ATF_TC_WITHOUT_HEAD(pass_but_fail_check);
50ATF_TC_BODY(pass_but_fail_check, tc)
51{
52 atf_tc_expect_pass();
53 atf_tc_fail_nonfatal("Some reason");
54}
55
56ATF_TC_WITHOUT_HEAD(fail_and_fail_requirement);
57ATF_TC_BODY(fail_and_fail_requirement, tc)
58{
59 atf_tc_expect_fail("Fail %s", "reason");
60 atf_tc_fail("The failure");
61 atf_tc_expect_pass();
62}
63
64ATF_TC_WITHOUT_HEAD(fail_and_fail_check);
65ATF_TC_BODY(fail_and_fail_check, tc)
66{
67 atf_tc_expect_fail("Fail first");
68 atf_tc_fail_nonfatal("abc");
69 atf_tc_expect_pass();
70
71 atf_tc_expect_fail("And fail again");
72 atf_tc_fail_nonfatal("def");
73 atf_tc_expect_pass();
74}
75
76ATF_TC_WITHOUT_HEAD(fail_but_pass);
77ATF_TC_BODY(fail_but_pass, tc)
78{
79 atf_tc_expect_fail("Fail first");
80 atf_tc_fail_nonfatal("abc");
81 atf_tc_expect_pass();
82
83 atf_tc_expect_fail("Will not fail");
84 atf_tc_expect_pass();
85
86 atf_tc_expect_fail("And fail again");
87 atf_tc_fail_nonfatal("def");
88 atf_tc_expect_pass();
89}
90
91ATF_TC_WITHOUT_HEAD(exit_any_and_exit);
92ATF_TC_BODY(exit_any_and_exit, tc)
93{
94 atf_tc_expect_exit(-1, "Call will exit");
95 exit(EXIT_SUCCESS);
96}
97
98ATF_TC_WITHOUT_HEAD(exit_code_and_exit);
99ATF_TC_BODY(exit_code_and_exit, tc)
100{
101 atf_tc_expect_exit(123, "Call will exit");
102 exit(123);
103}
104
105ATF_TC_WITHOUT_HEAD(exit_but_pass);
106ATF_TC_BODY(exit_but_pass, tc)
107{
108 atf_tc_expect_exit(-1, "Call won't exit");
109}
110
111ATF_TC_WITHOUT_HEAD(signal_any_and_signal);
112ATF_TC_BODY(signal_any_and_signal, tc)
113{
114 atf_tc_expect_signal(-1, "Call will signal");
115 kill(getpid(), SIGKILL);
116}
117
118ATF_TC_WITHOUT_HEAD(signal_no_and_signal);
119ATF_TC_BODY(signal_no_and_signal, tc)
120{
121 atf_tc_expect_signal(SIGHUP, "Call will signal");
122 kill(getpid(), SIGHUP);
123}
124
125ATF_TC_WITHOUT_HEAD(signal_but_pass);
126ATF_TC_BODY(signal_but_pass, tc)
127{
128 atf_tc_expect_signal(-1, "Call won't signal");
129}
130
131ATF_TC_WITHOUT_HEAD(death_and_exit);
132ATF_TC_BODY(death_and_exit, tc)
133{
134 atf_tc_expect_death("Exit case");
135 exit(123);
136}
137
138ATF_TC_WITHOUT_HEAD(death_and_signal);
139ATF_TC_BODY(death_and_signal, tc)
140{
141 atf_tc_expect_death("Signal case");
142 kill(getpid(), SIGKILL);
143}
144
145ATF_TC_WITHOUT_HEAD(death_but_pass);
146ATF_TC_BODY(death_but_pass, tc)
147{
148 atf_tc_expect_death("Call won't die");
149}
150
151ATF_TC(timeout_and_hang);
152ATF_TC_HEAD(timeout_and_hang, tc)
153{
154 atf_tc_set_md_var(tc, "timeout", "1");
155}
156ATF_TC_BODY(timeout_and_hang, tc)
157{
158 atf_tc_expect_timeout("Will overrun");
159 sleep(5);
160}
161
162ATF_TC(timeout_but_pass);
163ATF_TC_HEAD(timeout_but_pass, tc)
164{
165 atf_tc_set_md_var(tc, "timeout", "1");
166}
167ATF_TC_BODY(timeout_but_pass, tc)
168{
169 atf_tc_expect_timeout("Will just exit");
170}
171
172ATF_TP_ADD_TCS(tp)
173{
174 ATF_TP_ADD_TC(tp, pass_and_pass);
175 ATF_TP_ADD_TC(tp, pass_but_fail_requirement);
176 ATF_TP_ADD_TC(tp, pass_but_fail_check);
177 ATF_TP_ADD_TC(tp, fail_and_fail_requirement);
178 ATF_TP_ADD_TC(tp, fail_and_fail_check);
179 ATF_TP_ADD_TC(tp, fail_but_pass);
180 ATF_TP_ADD_TC(tp, exit_any_and_exit);
181 ATF_TP_ADD_TC(tp, exit_code_and_exit);
182 ATF_TP_ADD_TC(tp, exit_but_pass);
183 ATF_TP_ADD_TC(tp, signal_any_and_signal);
184 ATF_TP_ADD_TC(tp, signal_no_and_signal);
185 ATF_TP_ADD_TC(tp, signal_but_pass);
186 ATF_TP_ADD_TC(tp, death_and_exit);
187 ATF_TP_ADD_TC(tp, death_and_signal);
188 ATF_TP_ADD_TC(tp, death_but_pass);
189 ATF_TP_ADD_TC(tp, timeout_and_hang);
190 ATF_TP_ADD_TC(tp, timeout_but_pass);
191
192 return atf_no_error();
193}
